"Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr> Operator Service, which is delivered by\n"
"    Agilisys (a contractor employed by the <abbr title=\"The Legal Aid "
"Agency\">LAA</abbr> to Agilisys on behalf of Freedom Communications (a "
"contractor\n"
"    employed by the <abbr title=\"The Legal Aid Agency\">LAA</abbr> to "
"deliver the <abbr title=\"Civil Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr> Operator "
"Service)."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch yn cysylltu gyntaf â CLA, byddwch yn cyfathrebu â Gwasanaeth "
"Gweithredwyr CLA, sy’n cael ei ddarparu gan Agilisys ar ran Freedom "
"Communications (contractwr sy’n cael ei gyflogi gan yr LAA i ddarparu "
"Gwasanaeth Gweithredwyr CLA). "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:28
msgid "Complaints"
msgstr "Cwynion"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:30
msgid ""
"If you would like to make a complaint about this service or Civil Legal "
"Advice please contact <abbr title=\"Civil Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr> on "
"0345 345 4 345."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi’n dymuno gwneud cwyn am y gwasanaeth hwn neu Gyngor "
"Cyfreithiol Sifil, cysylltwch â CLA ar 0345 345 4 345"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:33
msgid "How is my privacy protected?"
msgstr "Sut yr ydych chi’n diogelu fy mhreifatrwydd?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:35
msgid ""
"Protecting your privacy is important to us. You can use this service to "
"find out if you might qualify for\n"
"    legal aid without providing any personal information that could "
"identify you."
msgstr ""
"Mae diogelu’ch preifatrwydd yn bwysig i ni. Gallwch chi ddefnyddio’r "
"gwasanaeth hwn i gael gwybod a allech fod yn gymwys i gael cymorth "
"cyfreithiol heb ddarparu unrhyw wybodaeth bersonol a allai ddangos pwy "
"ydych chi. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:40
msgid ""
"We only save the information you enter if you decide to request a "
"callback from a Civil Legal Advice\n"
"    operator."
msgstr ""
"Dim ond os byddwch chi’n penderfynu gofyn am gael galwad yn ôl gan un o "
"weithredwyr Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil y byddwn ni’n cadw’r wybodaeth yr "
"ydych chi’n ei rhoi. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:45
msgid ""
"At this point, you will need to tell us your name and phone number and "
"all the information you've entered will\n"
"    be stored when you click 'Submit your application'. We store this "
"information so that the operator can see it\n"
"    when they speak to you."
msgstr ""
"Yn awr, bydd angen i chi roi’ch enw a’ch rhif ffôn i ni a bydd yr holl "
"wybodaeth yr ydych wedi’i rhoi’n cael ei storio pan fyddwch chi’n clicio "
"ar ‘Cyflwyno’ch cais’. Rydyn ni’n storio’r wybodaeth hon fel y bydd y "
"gweithredwr yn gallu ei gweld wrth siarad â chi."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:51
msgid ""
"If you don't want to speak to an operator, you don't need to enter any "
"personal details and we don't store\n"
"    any of the information you have entered."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych chi am siarad â gweithredwr, ni fydd angen i chi roi unrhyw "
"fanylion personol a ni fyddwn ni’n storio unrhyw wybodaeth yr ydych chi "
"wedi’i rhoi."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:56
msgid ""
"To provide you with the best service that we can, Civil Legal Advice may "
"share some information about you\n"
"    with other organisations. But we will only do this if you have given "
"us permission."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn darparu’r gwasanaeth gorau posibl i chi, mae’n bosibl y bydd "
"Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil yn rhannu rhywfaint o wybodaeth amdanoch chi â "
"sefydliadau eraill. Ond dim ond os ydych chi wedi rhoi caniatâd i ni y "
"byddwn ni’n gwneud hyn. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:61
msgid ""
"In exceptional circumstances, we may share limited information about you "
"without your consent. This would\n"
"    only be to prevent fraud, help detect crime, if it is required by law"
" or by a court order or If we are\n"
"    very worried about your safety or the safety of others."
msgstr ""
"Mewn amgylchiadau eithriadol, gallwn ni rannu gwybodaeth benodol amdanoch"
" heb gael eich caniatâd. Yr unig reswm y bydden ni’n gwneud hyn yw er "
"mwyn atal twyll, helpu i ddarganfod troseddu, os yw’n ofynnol o dan y "
"gyfraith neu orchymyn llys neu os ydyn ni’n pryderu’n fawr am eich "
"diogelwch chi neu bobl eraill. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:67
msgid "Read the full Civil Legal Advice Privacy Statement here."
msgstr "Darllenwch Ddatganiad Preifatrwydd Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil yn llawn yma. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:71
msgid "Civil Legal Advice Privacy Statement"
msgstr "Datganiad Preifatrwydd Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:73
msgid ""
"In order to provide a service to you, Civil Legal Advice (<abbr "
"title=\"Civil Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr>)\n"
"    may need to view, collect, record and hold (‘process’) personal data "
"about you."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn darparu gwasanaeth i chi, mae’n bosibl y bydd angen i Gyngor "
"Cyfreithiol Sifil (CLA) weld, casglu, cofnodi a dal (‘prosesu’) data "
"personol amdanoch chi."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:77
msgid ""
"Personal data is information about you that can be used to identify you "
"in some way\n"
"    e.g. your name or telephone number. You can look at the\n"
"    <a "
"href=\"http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions"
"#personal-data\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">full legal "
"definition</a>."
msgstr ""
"Data personol yw gwybodaeth amdanoch chi y gellir ei defnyddio i’ch "
"adnabod mewn rhyw ffordd e.e. eich enw neu rif ffôn. Gallwch weld y "
"diffiniad cyfreithiol llawn yma: "
"http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions"
"#personal-data."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:82
msgid ""
"<abbr title=\"Civil Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr> is committed to protecting "
"your personal data and respecting your privacy.\n"
"    We are legally bound by the Data Protection Act 1998 to ensure that "
"we only use your personal\n"
"    data for the reasons we tell you about. We must also hold it securely."
msgstr ""
"Mae CLA wedi ymrwymo i ddiogelu’ch data personol a pharchu’ch "
"preifatrwydd. Rydym wedi cael ein rhwymo’n gyfreithiol gan Ddeddf Diogelu"
" Data 1998 i sicrhau mai dim ond am y rhesymau y byddwn yn eu rhoi i chi "
"y byddwn yn defnyddio’ch data personol. Hefyd rhaid i ni eu dal yn "
"ddiogel. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:87
msgid ""
"This statement explains how <abbr>CLA</abbr> will process any personal "
"data that we collect\n"
"    from you or that you provide to us."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r datganiad hwn yn egluro sut y bydd CLA yn prosesu unrhyw ddata "
"personol y byddwn yn eu casglu oddi wrthych neu y byddwch yn eu darparu i"
" ni."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:92
msgid "What is Civil Legal Advice?"
msgstr "Beth yw Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:94
msgid "is a national adviceline for England and Wales, paid for by Legal Aid."
msgstr ""
"Mae Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil (CLA) yn llinell gyngor cenedlaethol ar "
"gyfer Cymru a Lloegr sy’n cael ei hariannu drwy Gymorth Cyfreithiol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:97
msgid ""
"The Legal Aid Agency (<abbr title=\"The Legal Aid Agency\">LAA</abbr>) is"
" responsible for the <abbr>CLA</abbr>\n"
"    service and the Ministry of Justice (<abbr title=\"The Ministry of "
"Justice\">MoJ</abbr>) is the Data Controller\n"
"    for the purposes of the Data Protection Act 1998. They are "
"responsible for determining the purposes for which\n"
"    and the manner in which any personal data are, or are to be processed."
msgstr ""
"Yr Asiantaeth Cymorth Cyfreithiol (LAA) sy’n gyfrifol am wasanaeth CLA "
"a’r Weinyddiaeth Cyfiawnder yw’r Rheolydd Data i ddibenion Deddf Diogelu "
"Data 1998. Maent yn gyfrifol am bennu’r dibenion y mae neu y bydd unrhyw "
"ddata personol yn cael eu prosesu ar eu cyfer a’r ffordd o wneud hynny."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:103
msgid ""
"For a more comprehensive explanation see\n"
"    <a "
"href=\"http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions"
"#personal-data\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">this guide</a>."
msgstr ""
"Mae esboniad mwy cynhwysfawr ar gael drwy ddilyn y ddolen isod: "
"http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions"
"#personal-data."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:107
msgid ""
"The <abbr title=\"The Legal Aid Agency\">LAA</abbr> works with other "
"organisations who deliver the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service.\n"
"    For example when you first make contact with <abbr>CLA</abbr> you "
"will communicate with\n"
"    the <abbr>CLA</abbr> Operator Service, which is delivered by Agilisys"
"\n"
"    (a contractor employed by the <abbr title=\"The Legal Aid "
"Agency\">LAA</abbr> to [  ])."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r LAA yn cydweithio â sefydliadau eraill sy’n darparu gwasanaeth CLA."
" Er enghraifft, pan fyddwch yn cysylltu gyntaf â CLA, byddwch yn "
"cyfathrebu â Gwasanaeth Gweithredwyr CLA, sy’n cael ei ddarparu gan "
"Agilisys ar ran Freedom Communications (contractwr sy’n cael ei gyflogi "
"gan yr LAA i ddarparu Gwasanaeth Gweithredwyr CLA). "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:113
msgid ""
"If after contacting the <abbr>CLA</abbr> Operator Service it is "
"determined that you\n"
"    qualify for the <abbr>CLA</abbr> specialist advice service you may be"
" put through\n"
"    to one of a number of <abbr>CLA</abbr> Specialist Advice Providers. "
"If you do not qualify to receive\n"
"    <abbr>CLA</abbr> specialist advice we will inform you accordingly and"
"\n"
"    direct you to alternative help."
msgstr ""
"Os penderfynir, wedi i chi gysylltu â Gwasanaeth Gweithredwyr CLA, eich "
"bod yn gymwys i dderbyn gwasanaeth cynghori arbenigol CLA, gallech gael "
"eich trosglwyddo i un o nifer o Ddarparwyr Cyngor Arbenigol CLA.  Os nad "
"ydych yn gymwys i gael cyngor arbenigol CLA, byddwn yn rhoi gwybod i chi "
"am hynny ac yn eich cyfeirio at leoedd eraill sy’n cynnig help."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:120
msgid ""
"These organisations are Data Processors for the purposes of the Data "
"Protection Act 1998 which\n"
"    means that they process data on behalf of the <abbr>LAA</abbr> and "
"<abbr title=\"The Ministry of Justice\">MoJ</abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r sefydliadau hyn yn Broseswyr Data i ddibenion Deddf Diogelu Data "
"1998. Mae hyn yn golygu eu bod yn prosesu data ar ran yr LAA a’r "
"Weinyddiaeth Cyfiawnder. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:124
msgid ""
"The <abbr>CLA</abbr> service is committed to following this Privacy "
"Statement.\n"
"    <abbr>CLA</abbr> Specialists must also adhere to their own internal "
"privacy policy."
msgstr ""
"Mae gwasanaeth CLA wedi ymrwymo i gydymffurfio â’r Datganiad Preifatrwydd"
" hwn. Hefyd rhaid i Arbenigwyr CLA gydymffurfio â’u polisi preifatrwydd "
"mewnol eu hunain."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:129
msgid "What data will <abbr>CLA</abbr> collect?"
msgstr "Pa ddata y bydd CLA yn eu casglu?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:131
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will only collect the minimum amount of information "
"necessary in order\n"
"    to deliver the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service to you."
msgstr ""
"Dim ond y wybodaeth sydd ei hangen i ddarparu gwasanaeth CLA i chi y bydd"
" CLA yn ei chasglu."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:135
msgid "The kind of information <abbr>CLA</abbr> may collect about you includes:"
msgstr "Y math o wybodaeth y gall CLA ei chasglu amdanoch chi yw:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:139
msgid ""
"Personal details including your name, address, date of birth, contact "
"details, diversity\n"
"      monitoring information and national insurance number;"
msgstr ""
"Manylion personol gan gynnwys eich enw, cyfeiriad, dyddiad geni, manylion"
" cysylltu, gwybodaeth ar gyfer monitro amrywiaeth a’ch rhif yswiriant "
"gwladol;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:143
msgid "Financial information needed to determine if you qualify for legal aid;"
msgstr ""
"Gwybodaeth ariannol sydd ei hangen i bennu a ydych chi’n gymwys i gael "
"cymorth cyfreithiol;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:146
msgid ""
"Reason for contacting <abbr>CLA</abbr>, such as the nature of your "
"problem or specific details about your situation;"
msgstr ""
"Y rheswm dros gysylltu â CLA, er enghraifft, natur eich problem neu "
"fanylion penodol am eich sefyllfa;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:149
msgid ""
"Details of any specific needs that you may have in order to access the "
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> service;"
msgstr ""
"Manylion am unrhyw anghenion penodol sydd gennych er mwyn defnyddio "
"gwasanaeth CLA;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:152
msgid ""
"Responses to any customer satisfaction survey or details of any feedback,"
" complaints or requests\n"
"      for a review of our decision about whether you qualify for legal "
"aid."
msgstr ""
"Ymatebion i unrhyw arolwg o fodlonrwydd cwsmeriaid neu fanylion am unrhyw"
" adborth, cwynion neu geisiadau am adolygu ein penderfyniad ynghylch a "
"ydych chi’n gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:157
msgid ""
"The amount of information <abbr>CLA</abbr> will collect will depend on "
"whether you qualify for the <abbr>CLA</abbr>\n"
"    service and/or your specific needs. For example you will be asked to "
"provide more information\n"
"    before we can transfer you through to a <abbr>CLA</abbr> Specialist."
msgstr ""
"Bydd maint y wybodaeth y mae CLA yn ei chasglu’n dibynnu ar ba un a ydych"
" chi’n gymwys i gael gwasanaeth CLA neu beidio a/neu eich anghenion "
"penodol. Er enghraifft, byddwn ni’n gofyn i chi ddarparu rhagor o "
"wybodaeth cyn eich trosglwyddo i un o Arbenigwyr CLA."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:163
msgid "What does <abbr>CLA</abbr> use the data for?"
msgstr "Ar gyfer beth y mae CLA yn defnyddio’r data?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:164
msgid "collects and records information about you to:"
msgstr "Mae CLA yn casglu ac yn cofnodi gwybodaeth amdanoch chi er mwyn:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:166
msgid "Work out whether you qualify for legal aid"
msgstr "Gweithio allan a ydych chi’n gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:167
msgid "Provide information and/or advice services to you"
msgstr "Darparu gwasanaethau gwybodaeth a/neu gyngor i chi"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:168
msgid "Save you from repeating information every time you contact us"
msgstr "Eich arbed rhag ailadrodd gwybodaeth bob tro y byddwch chi’n cysylltu â ni"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:169
msgid "Help us monitor and improve our service"
msgstr "Ein helpu i fonitro a gwella ein gwasanaeth "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:171
msgid ""
"Build statistics about the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service, monitor fraud and "
"justify public expenditure.\n"
"      This information is collated in an anonymous format."
msgstr ""
"Cael ystadegau am wasanaeth CLA, monitro twyll a chyfiawnhau gwariant "
"cyhoeddus. Mae’r wybodaeth hon yn cael ei chasglu heb gynnwys enwau. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:175
msgid ""
"Collect views on the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service and any improvements "
"considered necessary.\n"
"      Where consent is provided <abbr>CLA</abbr> User contact details may"
" be passed onto an independent research agency."
msgstr ""
"Casglu barn am wasanaeth CLA ac unrhyw welliannau sydd eu hangen. Os bydd"
" defnyddwyr gwasanaeth CLA yn cydsynio, gellir trosglwyddo eu manylion "
"cysylltu i asiantaeth ymchwil annibynnol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:178
msgid "Prevent or detect crime or fraud"
msgstr "Atal neu ddarganfod troseddu neu dwyll"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:181
msgid ""
"Given the purposes for which your personal data may be used (as referred "
"to above)\n"
"    it is essential that the information you provide is accurate and "
"complete."
msgstr ""
"Oherwydd y dibenion y gellir defnyddio eich data personol ar eu cyfer "
"(sydd wedi’u nodi uchod), mae’n hanfodol eich bod yn darparu gwybodaeth "
"sy’n gywir a chyflawn."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:186
msgid "How does <abbr>CLA</abbr> collect your personal data and keep it safe?"
msgstr "Sut y mae CLA yn casglu’ch data personol ac yn eu cadw’n ddiogel?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:188
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> may collect personal data about you by phone, online, "
"email or post (see table below).\n"
"    Any personal data will be recorded and stored within a secure system "
"that meets required Government standards."
msgstr ""
"Gall CLA gasglu data personol amdanoch chi dros y ffôn, ar-lein, drwy’r "
"post a’r e-bost (gweler y tabl isod). Bydd unrhyw ddata personol yn cael "
"eu cofnodi a’u storio mewn system ddiogel sy’n cyrraedd safonau sydd "
"wedi’u gosod gan y Llywodraeth."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:192
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will be able to view and verify the information that you"
" provide and where\n"
"    necessary will amend it to maintain its accuracy."
msgstr ""
"Bydd CLA yn gallu gweld a dilysu’r wybodaeth yr ydych chi’n ei darparu "
"ac, os bydd angen, bydd yn ei newid er mwyn ei chadw’n gywir."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:196
msgid ""
"The minimum amount of personal data that <abbr>CLA</abbr> will ask to "
"collect is your name and one other piece\n"
"    of personal information that could be used to identify you e.g. "
"postcode, date of birth or telephone number."
msgstr ""
"Y data personol lleiaf y bydd CLA yn gofyn am eu casglu yw’ch enw ac un "
"eitem arall o wybodaeth bersonol i’w defnyddio i’ch adnabod os bydd angen"
" e.e. cod post, dyddiad geni neu rif ffôn."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:200
msgid ""
"All personal data will be stored on secure servers in the UK. It may also"
" be stored outside of Europe,\n"
"    where it could be viewed by our staff or specialist providers."
msgstr ""
"Bydd yr holl ddata personol yn cael eu storio ar weinyddion diogel yn y "
"DU. Gellir eu storio y tu allan i Ewrop hefyd, lle y bydd ein staff neu "
"ddarparwyr arbenigol yn gallu eu gweld. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:204
msgid ""
"By submitting your personal data, you agree to information being "
"recorded, used and stored\n"
"    as outlined in this Privacy Statement."
msgstr ""
"Drwy gyflwyno’ch data personol, rydych chi’n cytuno i’r wybodaeth gael ei"
" chofnodi, ei defnyddio a’i storio’n unol â’r Datganiad Preifatrwydd hwn."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:208
msgid "How we collect and store your personal data"
msgstr "Sut yr ydym yn casglu ac yn storio’ch data personol"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:211
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "Ffôn"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:213
msgid ""
"When you call <abbr>CLA</abbr> we will record relevant personal data that"
" you provide within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        We may also record your calls. But you can choose to opt out of "
"this or choose whether or not\n"
"        to continue with the call.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        If you leave <abbr>CLA</abbr> a voice message we will record the "
"minimum amount of information\n"
"        required in order to contact you back."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch chi’n ffonio CLA, byddwn ni’n cofnodi data personol "
"perthnasol yr ydych chi’n eu rhoi mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Gallwn "
"recordio’ch galwadau hefyd. Ond cewch chi ddewis peidio ag ymuno â hyn "
"neu ddewis a ydych chi am barhau â’r alwad neu beidio. Os byddwch chi’n "
"gadael neges llais i CLA, byddwn ni’n cofnodi’r lleiaf o wybodaeth sydd "
"ei hangen i gysylltu â chi wedyn. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:223
msgid "Online"
msgstr "Ar-lein"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:225
msgid ""
"When you contact <abbr>CLA</abbr> online the personal data that you "
"provide will be recorded within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        Please note that transmitting information over the internet is "
"generally not completely secure, and\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> can’t guarantee the security of your data. Any "
"data you transmit is at your own risk.\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> have procedures and security features in place "
"to keep your data secure once we receive it."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch chi’n cysylltu â CLA ar-lein, bydd y data personol yr ydych "
"chi’n eu darparu’n cael eu cofnodi mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Cofiwch "
"nad yw gwybodaeth sy’n cael ei throsglwyddo dros y rhyngrwyd yn hollol "
"ddiogel yn gyffredinol, ac nid yw CLA yn gallu gwarantu y bydd eich "
"data’n ddiogel. Ar eich menter eich hun y byddwch chi’n trosglwyddo "
"unrhyw ddata. Mae CLA wedi rhoi gweithdrefnau a chyfleusterau diogelwch "
"ar waith i gadw’ch data’n ddiogel wedi i ni eu cael."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:233
msgid "Email"
msgstr "E-bost"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:235
msgid ""
"Transmitting information via email is generally not completely secure, "
"and <abbr>CLA</abbr> can’t guarantee the\n"
"        security of your data. Any data you transmit is at your own risk."
"\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> have procedures and security features in place "
"to keep your data secure once we receive it.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        When you email <abbr>CLA</abbr>, relevant personal data that you "
"provide will be recorded within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> may monitor and store both your incoming and "
"outgoing emails. We may also use blocking software,"
msgstr ""
"Nid yw gwybodaeth sy’n cael ei throsglwyddo drwy’r e-bost yn hollol "
"ddiogel yn gyffredinol, ac nid yw CLA yn gallu gwarantu y bydd eich "
"data’n ddiogel. Ar eich menter eich hun y byddwch chi’n trosglwyddo "
"unrhyw ddata. Mae CLA wedi rhoi gweithdrefnau a chyfleusterau diogelwch "
"ar waith i gadw’ch data’n ddiogel wedi i ni eu cael. Pan fyddwch chi’n "
"anfon neges e-bost i CLA, bydd data personol perthnasol yr ydych chi’n eu"
" darparu yn cael eu cofnodi mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Mae CLA yn "
"gallu monitro a storio negeseuon e-bost oddi wrthych chi ac atoch chi. "
"Hefyd gallwn ddefnyddio meddalwedd rhwystro. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:246
msgid "Post"
msgstr "Post"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:248
msgid ""
"When <abbr>CLA</abbr> receives post we may record relevant personal data "
"included within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> may also retain original hard-copies of "
"information submitted by you. This must be stored in a locked\n"
"        filing cabinet. Digital copies of letters may be scanned and "
"stored."
msgstr ""
"Pan fydd CLA yn derbyn llythyrau, gallwn ni gofnodi data personol "
"perthnasol sydd ynddynt mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Hefyd gall CLA gadw"
" llythyrau gwreiddiol sy’n cynnwys gwybodaeth a gyflwynwyd gennych chi. "
"Rhaid storio’r rhain mewn cwpwrdd ffeiliau sydd wedi’i gloi. Gellir "
"sganio copïau digidol o lythyrau a’u storio. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:257
msgid "Keeping your personal data safe from others"
msgstr "Cadw’ch data personol yn ddiogel oddi wrth eraill"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:260
msgid "Repeat Contacts"
msgstr "Ailgysylltu"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:262
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will not disclose any personal information to anyone "
"contacting the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service until\n"
"        they have successfully verified that their identity matches that "
"of an existing record."
msgstr ""
"Ni fydd CLA yn datgelu unrhyw wybodaeth bersonol i rywun sy’n cysylltu â "
"gwasanaeth CLA nes ei fod wedi cadarnhau bod ei hunaniaeth yn cyfateb i "
"gofnod sy’n bodoli. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:267
msgid "Third-parties"
msgstr "Trydydd parti"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:269
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will accept contact made by a third-party on behalf of "
"another person. The third party has to\n"
"        demonstrate they have appropriate authority to act on your "
"behalf.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> must record the relationship between the third-"
"party and the individual seeking advice\n"
"        and whether they are authorised to act on their behalf.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        They must also agree a password to verify the identity of the "
"third-party if they contact the service again."
msgstr ""
"Bydd CLA yn cydnabod trydydd parti sy’n cysylltu ar ran person arall. "
"Mae’n rhaid i’r trydydd parti ddangos bod ganddynt yr awdurdod priodol i "
"weithredu ar eich rhan. Rhaid i CLA gofnodi’r berthynas rhwng y trydydd "
"parti a’r unigolyn sy’n gofyn am gyngor ac a yw’r trydydd parti wedi’i "
"awdurdodi i weithredu ar ei ran. Hefyd rhaid i CLA gytuno ar gyfrinair er"
" mwyn gwirio hunaniaeth y trydydd parti os bydd yn cysylltu â’r "
"gwasanaeth eto."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:279
msgid "Outgoing Communications"
msgstr "Anfon negeseuon allan"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:281
msgid "<abbr>CLA</abbr> may need to contact you directly."
msgstr "Mae’n bosibl y bydd angen i CLA gysylltu â chi’n uniongyrchol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:283
msgid ""
"In order to protect privacy <abbr>CLA</abbr> will always check with you "
"what forms of outgoing communication are acceptable and appropriate and "
"whether messages can be left."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn diogelu preifatrwydd, bydd CLA bob amser yn gofyn pa ddulliau o "
"gyfathrebu â chi sy’n dderbyniol a phriodol ac a allwn ni adael "
"negeseuon. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:285
msgid "When making outgoing calls to you <abbr>CLA</abbr> will ensure that:"
msgstr "Pan fydd CLA yn eich ffonio, bydd yn sicrhau: "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:288
msgid ""
"Call backs are only made where you have agreed to this. Authorised third "
"parties\n"
"            acting on your behalf can give agreement."
msgstr ""
"Mai dim ond os ydych chi wedi cytuno ar hynny y byddwn ni’n ffonio’n ôl. "
"Gall trydydd parti gytuno ar hyn os yw wedi’i awdurdodi i weithredu ar "
"eich rhan."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:292
msgid ""
"Where a call back is made to you and there is no answer and a message "
"taker is available,\n"
"            no message will be left unless you have previously given "
"specific instructions that this would be acceptable."
msgstr ""
"Os yw’n ffonio’n ôl ac nad oes ateb, a bod recordydd negeseuon ar gael, "
"na fydd yn gadael neges oni bai eich bod wedi rhoi cyfarwyddiadau penodol"
" cyn hynny fod hyn yn dderbyniol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:296
msgid ""
"Where the phone is answered and someone other than you answers the phone "
"and says that you are\n"
"            unavailable or asks who is calling, <abbr>CLA</abbr> will "
"state that the call is confidential and will not say\n"
"            that they are calling from <abbr>CLA</abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Os bydd rhywun heblaw chi’n ateb y ffôn ac yn dweud nad ydych chi ar gael"
" neu’n gofyn pwy sy’n galw, y bydd CLA yn dweud bod yr alwad yn "
"gyfrinachol ac na fydd yn dweud ei fod yn ffonio o CLA."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:306
msgid "How we use cookies"
msgstr "Sut yr ydym yn defnyddio cwcis"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:308
msgid ""
"When you use our online services we may store a small file, known as a "
"cookie, on your\n"
"    <abbr title=\"Personal Computer\">PC</abbr> or digital device."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch chi’n defnyddio ein gwasanaethau ar-lein, mae’n bosibl y "
"byddwn ni’n storio ffeil fach, sy’n cael ei galw’n ‘cwci’, ar eich "
"cyfrifiadur personol neu ddyfais ddigidol. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:311
msgid "You may see a message before we store a cookie on your computer."
msgstr ""
"Mae’n bosibl y byddwch chi’n gweld neges cyn i ni storio cwci ar eich "
"cyfrifiadur."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:312
msgid "The cookies are not used to identify you personally."
msgstr "Nid yw’r cwcis yn cael eu defnyddio i’ch adnabod yn bersonol.."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:313
msgid "We use these cookies to:"
msgstr "Rydyn ni’n defnyddio’r cwcis hyn er mwyn:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:315
msgid ""
"Help your <abbr>PC</abbr> or digital device to interact with us more "
"quickly"
msgstr ""
"Helpu’ch cyfrifiadur personol neu ddyfais ddigidol i ryngweithio â ni’n "
"fwy cyflym "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:316
msgid ""
"Measure how you use our service so it can be updated and improved based "
"on your needs"
msgstr ""
"Asesu sut yr ydych chi’n defnyddio ein gwasanaeth er mwyn ei ddiweddaru "
"a’i wella ar sail eich anghenion"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:317
msgid ""
"Remember the notifications you’ve seen so that we don’t show them to you "
"again"
msgstr ""
"Cofio’r negeseuon yr ydych chi wedi’u gweld fel na fyddwn ni’n eu dangos "
"i chi eto"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:319
msgid ""
"Remember how you progress through our service. These cookies don't store "
"your personal\n"
"      data and are deleted once you've completed the service."
msgstr ""
"Cofio’r camau yr ydych chi’n eu cymryd drwy ein gwasanaeth. Nid yw’r "
"cwcis hyn yn storio’ch data personol a byddan nhw’n cael eu dileu ar ôl i"
" chi orffen defnyddio’r gwasanaeth."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:323
msgid ""
"Protect your security by ensuring that third parties cannot create sites "
"that pose as\n"
"      a gov.uk service in an attempt to gather your information."
msgstr ""
"Eich cadw’n ddiogel drwy sicrhau na fydd trydydd parti yn gallu creu "
"gwefannau sy’n honni bod yn wasanaeth gov.uk er mwyn casglu’ch "
"gwybodaeth. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:328
msgid ""
"You can read more about <a href=\"%(cookie_url)s\">how cookies are "
"used</a>."
msgstr ""
"Mae rhagor o wybodaeth yma am y ffordd y     <a "
"href=\"https://www.gov.uk/help/cookies\"  rel=\"external\" "
"target=\"_blank\">mae cwcis yn cael eu defnyddio ar gov.uk</a>."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:331
msgid ""
"You can read about\n"
"    <a href=\"http://www.aboutcookies.org/\" rel=\"external\" "
"target=\"_blank\">how to manage cookies</a>."
msgstr "Mae gwybodaeth am ffyrdd o reoli cwcis yma: http://www.aboutcookies.org/"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:336
msgid "When will we share information about you outside <abbr>CLA</abbr>?"
msgstr "Pryd y byddwn ni’n rhannu gwybodaeth amdanoch chi y tu allan i CLA?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:337
msgid ""
"Confidentiality means ensuring information is only accessible by those "
"allowed to have access to it."
msgstr ""
"Mae cyfrinachedd yn golygu sicrhau mai dim ond y rheini sydd â hawl i "
"weld gwybodaeth a fydd yn ei gweld."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:339
msgid ""
"We want to keep your contact with <abbr>CLA</abbr> confidential, which "
"means you can feel safe talking to us.\n"
"    But we sometimes need to share some information outside "
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> which we explain below."
msgstr ""
"Rydyn ni am gadw’ch cysylltiad â CLA yn gyfrinachol: mae hyn yn golygu y "
"byddwch chi’n gallu teimlo’n ddiogel wrth siarad â ni. Ond weithiau bydd "
"angen i ni rannu rhywfaint o wybodaeth y tu allan i CLA. Rydyn ni’n "
"egluro hyn isod."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:343
msgid ""
"In order to provide you with the best service that we can we may share "
"some information about\n"
"    you with the organisations mentioned below. But we will only do this "
"if you have given us consent\n"
"    when the operator asks for it."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn darparu’r gwasanaeth gorau posibl i chi, mae’n bosibl y byddwn "
"ni’n rhannu rhywfaint o wybodaeth amdanoch chi â’r sefydliadau sydd "
"wedi’u henwi isod. Ond ni fyddwn ni’n gwneud hyn oni bai’ch bod chi wedi "
"rhoi caniatâd i ni pan fydd y gweithredwr yn gofyn amdano."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:350 cla_public/templates/privacy.html:397
msgid "Who"
msgstr "Pwy"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:351 cla_public/templates/privacy.html:398
msgid "Why"
msgstr "Pam"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:357
msgid ""
"External research organisations engaged by <abbr title=\"The Legal Aid "
"Agency\">LAA</abbr>\n"
"          or <abbr title=\"The Ministry of Justice\">MoJ</abbr>"
msgstr ""
"Sefydliadau ymchwil allanol sy’n gweithio i’r LAA neu’r Weinyddiaeth "
"Cyfiawnder "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:361
msgid ""
"To inform future government policy on legal aid. Such research will not "
"identify\n"
"          individuals whose data has been used for research purposes."
msgstr ""
"I gyfrannu at lunio polisi llywodraeth ar gymorth cyfreithiol yn y "
"dyfodol. Ni fydd ymchwil o’r fath yn enwi unigolion y mae eu data wedi’u "
"defnyddio ar gyfer ymchwil."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:367 cla_public/templates/privacy.html:404
msgid "Other government organisations"
msgstr "Sefydliadau llywodraeth eraill"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:370
msgid ""
"To verify information provided by you and check whether you qualify for "
"legal aid."
msgstr ""
"I ddilysu gwybodaeth yr ydych chi wedi’i darparu a gwirio a ydych chi’n "
"gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:375
msgid "Other advice organisations"
msgstr "Sefydliadau cynghori eraill"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:378
msgid "To help you get further help and advice from appropriate organisations."
msgstr "I’ch helpu i gael help a chyngor pellach gan sefydliadau priodol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:385
msgid ""
"In exceptional circumstances we may share limited information without "
"your consent,\n"
"    for example if it is a legal requirement or a court compels us to do "
"so."
msgstr ""
"Mewn amgylchiadau eithriadol, gallwn ni rannu gwybodaeth benodol heb gael"
" cydsyniad gennych chi, er enghraifft, os yw’n ofyniad cyfreithiol neu os"
" bydd llys yn ein gorfodi i wneud hynny. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:388
msgid "If we do this we will wherever possible:"
msgstr "Os byddwn ni’n gwneud hyn, lle bynnag y bo modd, byddwn:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:390
msgid "Talk to you first"
msgstr "yn siarad â chi’n gyntaf "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:391
msgid "Give you as much control as possible over how we do this"
msgstr ""
"yn rhoi cymaint o reolaeth â phosibl dros y ffordd y byddwn ni’n gwneud "
"hyn"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:392
msgid "Only share information on a ‘need to know’ basis."
msgstr "yn rhannu gwybodaeth ar sail ‘yr angen i wybod’ yn unig. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:407
msgid "To prevent fraud and help detect crime."
msgstr "I atal twyll a helpu i ddarganfod troseddu"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:409
msgid "Or where it is required by law or by a court order"
msgstr "Neu os yw’n ofynnol o dan y gyfraith neu orchymyn llys"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:414
msgid "External protection organisations"
msgstr "Sefydliadau diogelu allanol"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:417
msgid ""
"If we are very worried about your safety or the safety of other people we"
" may need to let others know.\n"
"          <br><br>\n"
"          For example if we think it necessary in order to protect a "
"child, young person or vulnerable adult\n"
"          from abuse or if we think that there is an immediate risk of "
"harm."
msgstr ""
"Os ydyn ni’n pryderu’n fawr am eich diogelwch chi neu bobl eraill, mae’n "
"bosibl y bydd angen i ni roi gwybod i bobl eraill. Er enghraifft, os ydyn"
" ni’n credu ei bod yn angenrheidiol er mwyn diogelu plentyn, person ifanc"
" neu oedolyn agored i niwed rhag cael ei gam-drin neu os ydyn ni’n credu "
"bod rhywun mewn perygl uniongyrchol o gael niwed. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:427
msgid "Requests to view and amend <abbr>CLA</abbr> Data"
msgstr "Ceisiadau i weld a diwygio Data CLA"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:428
msgid ""
"You have the right to request details about the personal information "
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> holds about you."
msgstr ""
"Mae gennych chi hawl i ofyn am fanylion y wybodaeth bersonol y mae CLA yn"
" ei dal amdanoch chi. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:429
msgid ""
"You can also request us to correct any personal information if it is "
"found to be inaccurate or out of date."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch chi hefyd ofyn i ni gywiro unrhyw wybodaeth bersonol os gwelir ei"
" bod yn anghywir neu wedi dyddio."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:432
msgid "Requests to view personal data held by <abbr>CLA</abbr>"
msgstr "Ceisiadau i weld data personol sy’n cael eu dal gan CLA"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:433
msgid ""
"If you want to view your record, please make a request in writing "
"including your."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi am weld eich cofnod, gwnewch gais drwy lythyr gan gynnwys "
"eich: "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:437
msgid "Date of birth"
msgstr "Dyddiad geni"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:438
msgid "What you contacted <abbr>CLA</abbr> about"
msgstr "Y mater yr oeddech chi wedi cysylltu â CLA yn ei gylch"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:439
msgid "When you contacted <abbr>CLA</abbr>"
msgstr "Pryd yr oeddech chi wedi cysylltu â CLA"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:440
msgid "What information you want to see"
msgstr "Pa wybodaeth yr ydych chi am ei gweld"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:442
msgid ""
"Any additional information that might help us to check your identity e.g."
" <abbr>CLA</abbr> case reference number.\n"
"      This is to help us protect your privacy by ensuring that we only "
"give data out to the person it relates to\n"
"      (or their appropriately authorised representative)."
msgstr ""
"Unrhyw wybodaeth ychwanegol i’n helpu i wirio pwy ydych chi e.e. rhif "
"cyfeirio achos CLA. Bydd hyn yn ein helpu i ddiogelu’ch preifatrwydd drwy"
" sicrhau mai dim ond i’r person y mae’r data’n ymwneud ag ef (neu "
"gynrychiolydd sydd wedi’i awdurdodi’n briodol) y byddwn ni’n rhoi’r data."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:448
msgid ""
"Please note that we cannot give out any information unless the details "
"that you provide match our records.\n"
"    If you used a fake name or pseudonym when you contacted "
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> you will need to prove your identity."
msgstr ""
"Ni fyddwn ni’n gallu rhoi unrhyw wybodaeth oni bai fod y manylion yr "
"ydych chi’n eu darparu’n cyfateb i’r rhai yn ein cofnodion. Os oeddech "
"chi wedi defnyddio ffugenw wrth gysylltu â CLA, bydd angen i chi brofi "
"pwy ydych chi."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:452
msgid ""
"If you gave us enough information to identify you, <abbr>CLA</abbr> will "
"send you your personal information as soon as\n"
"    possible but within a maximum of 40 days."
msgstr ""
"Os byddwch chi wedi rhoi digon o wybodaeth i’ch adnabod, bydd CLA yn "
"anfon eich gwybodaeth bersonol atoch chi cyn gynted â phosibl ac o fewn "
"40 diwrnod ar y mwyaf."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:456
msgid ""
"You can contact us by email at <a class=\"email\" "
"href=\"mailto:data.access@justice.gsi.gov.uk\">data.access@justice.gsi.gov.uk</a>"
" or in writing to"
msgstr ""
"Gallwch chi gysylltu â ni drwy’r e-bost yn data.access@justice.gsi.gov.uk"
" neu drwy lythyr yn "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:470
msgid "Requests to delete personal data"
msgstr "Ceisiadau i ddileu data personol"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:472
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will only keep a record of your personal data where you "
"have consented to this and we will handle it carefully."
msgstr ""
"Dim ond os ydych chi wedi cydsynio i hynny y bydd CLA yn cadw cofnod o’ch"
" data personol a byddwn ni’n ei drin yn ofalus."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:475
msgid ""
"We will consider requests to delete some or all of your personal data but"
" please note that as a minimum <abbr>CLA</abbr> will usually retain:"
msgstr ""
"Byddwn ni’n ystyried ceisiadau am ddileu rhai neu’r cyfan o’ch data "
"personol ond fel arfer bydd CLA yn cadw’r canlynol o leiaf:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:479
msgid ""
"For everyone that uses our service we will retain a name and one other "
"piece of personal data e.g.\n"
"      date of birth and details of what we did for you"
msgstr ""
"Ar gyfer pawb sy’n defnyddio ein gwasanaeth, byddwn yn cadw enw ac un "
"eitem arall o ddata personol e.e. dyddiad geni a manylion y gwasanaeth yr"
" ydyn ni wedi’i roi i chi "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:483
msgid ""
"For everyone that asks <abbr>CLA</abbr> to check whether they qualify for"
" legal aid in order to seek advice from a\n"
"      <abbr>CLA</abbr> Specialist we will also retain details of any "
"financial information and case details used to prove that\n"
"      you qualify for legal aid."
msgstr ""
"Ar gyfer pawb sy’n gofyn i CLA wirio a ydyn nhw’n gymwys i gael cymorth "
"cyfreithiol er mwyn gofyn am gyngor gan un o Arbenigwyr CLA, byddwn ni "
"hefyd yn cadw manylion am unrhyw wybodaeth ariannol a manylion achosion a"
" oedd wedi’u defnyddio i brofi eich bod yn gymwys i gael cymorth "
"cyfreithiol. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:489
msgid ""
"Please note that if you qualify to receive advice from a <abbr>CLA</abbr>"
" Specialist, they will also need to retain\n"
"    additional personal data about you within their own Case Handling "
"System. Such data shall be sufficient\n"
"    to justify the provision of legal aid advice and meet professional "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Os byddwch chi’n gymwys i gael cyngor gan un o Arbenigwyr CLA, bydd angen"
" hefyd iddo gadw data personol ychwanegol amdanoch chi yn ei System "
"Trafod Achosion ei hun.  Rhaid cadw digon o ddata o’r fath i gyfiawnhau "
"darparu cyngor drwy gymorth cyfreithiol ac i gwrdd â gofynion "
"proffesiynol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:495
msgid "Changes to the statement"
msgstr "Newidiadau yn y datganiad"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:497
msgid ""
"This policy is under regular review. Any changes made to the privacy "
"policy will be posted here and,\n"
"    where appropriate, <abbr>CLA</abbr> staff will be notified by email."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r polisi hwn yn cael ei adolygu’n rheolaidd. Bydd unrhyw newidiadau "
"yn y polisi preifatrwydd yn cael eu dangos yma ac, os yw’n briodol, bydd "
"staff CLA yn cael eu hysbysu drwy’r e-bost"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:502
msgid "Complaints about this statement"
msgstr "Cwynion am y datganiad hwn"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:504
msgid ""
"If you would like to make a complaint about this statement and how it "
"applies to you then please\n"
"    contact <abbr title=\"Civil Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr> on <span "
"class=\"tel\">0345 345 4 345</span>."
msgstr ""
